# CLAUDE.md

This repository uses the Agent Harness starter kit.

## Operating Rules

- Work from the repository's existing patterns before introducing new abstractions.
- Keep secrets out of source. Never print `.env*`, `secrets/`, private keys, or token values.
- Use an isolated worktree for code changes when multiple agents may work concurrently.
- For high-risk changes, record a short plan and route to the relevant specialist before writing code.
- Treat `.agent-harness/*.json` as the local source of truth for routing, domains, risk, and hook mode.

## Verification

Use the project's native checks. At minimum, run the narrowest relevant test and note any skipped validation.

## Local Harness Files

- `.agent-harness/config.json`
- `.agent-harness/agent-registry.json`
- `.agent-harness/domains.json`
- `.agent-harness/risk-rules.json`
